{"word":"H5301 - נָפַח - nâphach - naw-fakh' - Blow","slug":"H5301","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָפַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâphach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-fakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05E4;&#x05D7; - na&#x0302;phach</b> - <i>naw-fakh'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>puff</i>, in various applications (literally, to <i>inflate</i>, <i>blow</i> hard, <i>scatter</i>, <i>kindle</i>, <i>expire</i>; figuratively, to <i>disesteem</i>): - blow, breath, give up, cause to lose [life], seething, snuff."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4646\">H4646</a>, <a href=\"#/H4647\">H4647</a>, <a href=\"#/H5300\">H5300</a>, <a href=\"#/H5302\">H5302</a>, <a href=\"#/H5304\">H5304</a>, <a href=\"#/H5306\">H5306</a>, <a href=\"#/H5887\">H5887</a>, <a href=\"#/H8598\">H8598</a>, <a href=\"#/H8599\">H8599</a>"}]}